title: HCF-001 - Charity Picks
body:
50% of profits generated by the Hector Merch Store are donated to charity. Investors can choose which charity they would like to support by voting in HCF (Hector Charity Fund) votes like this one.

HCF votes to choose which charity we support will take place every 3 months.

In this round of voting, the winning charity will be supported from Jan 1st 2022 until April 1st 2022, when a new vote will take place.

Please research each charity before making your choice.

Charities:
- Rainforest Partnership
https://www.rainforestpartnership.org/

- Wonder Foundation
https://wonderfoundation.org.uk/

- Childhood Leukemia Foundation
https://www.clf4kids.org/

- Animal Equality
https://animalequality.org/

- Global Fund For Children
https://globalfundforchildren.org/
